{{Quote|We Tanwas are just Tans with an extra syllable picked up during some civil war or other.|Captain Suz Tanwa's Hunt Log|<ref name="Wizards">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040819yavin5|series=Yavin: The Big Red One|text=Part 5: Twenty-Two Catch}}</ref>}}
The '''Tan Clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]] during the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] period. In the aftermath of a civil war, an additional "wa" syllable was added to form a new clan, the [[Tanwa Clan|Tanwa]].<ref name="Wizards" />

The most notable member of this clan was [[Suvam Tan]], operator of [[Yavin Station]] in the [[Yavin system/Legends|Yavin system]].<ref name="Wizards" />

